      • populateCollection

        protected void populateCollection(Collection col,
                      Object o,
                      int varDepth)
        Add each element of the collection as a new vertex connected to the object o
        Parameters:
        col - collection with the JBioWH entities to be added as new vertexes
        o - JBioWH entity which is a vertex that is connected to all elements in the collection
        varDepth - the recursive depth for parent level

      • populateCollection

        protected void populateCollection(Collection col,
                      Object o,
                      int varDepth,
                      Object weightObject)
        Add each element of the collection as a new vertex connected to the object o in a weighted graph
        Parameters:
        col - collection with the JBioWH entities to be added as new vertexes
        o - JBioWH entity which is a vertex that is connected to all elements in the collection
        varDepth - the recursive depth for parent level
        weightObject - the object to increment the edge weight

      • addBioWHNewVertex

        protected void addBioWHNewVertex(Object source,
                     Object dest,
                     int varDepth)
        Add the vertex dest and create the edge with the vertex source. If the vertex already exist then just the edge is created
        Parameters:
        source - source vertex to be connected with the dest vertex
        dest - destination vertex to be connected with the source vertex
        varDepth - the recursive depth for parent level

      • addBioWHNewVertex

        protected void addBioWHNewVertex(Object source,
                     Object dest,
                     int varDepth,
                     Object weightObject)
        Add the vertex dest and create the edge with the vertex source. If the vertex already exist then just the edge is created. This method verify if the edge is created then increment the weight of this edge
        Parameters:
        source - source vertex to be connected with the dest vertex
        dest - destination vertex to be connected with the source vertex
        varDepth - the recursive depth for parent level
        weightObject - the MIF25 interaction that report the protein-protein interaction
